<span class="video-ionc"></span>
“燃灯”校长张桂梅
</p>
<p align="center">她</p>
<p align="center">像一盏明灯</p>
<p align="center">在漆黑的夜里</p>
<p align="center">为大山女孩</p>
<p align="center">照亮人生前路</p>
<p align="center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200911/c523c0aa93ac4da8bc79b865d385f7bb.gif" /></p>
<p align="center">她</p>
<p align="center">四处奔走</p>
